      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "If a $2 \\times 2$ augmented matrix is $\\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 2 & | & 5 \\\\ 0 & 0 & | & 7 \\end{bmatrix}$, how many solutions are there?",
