        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "The second row translates to $0 = 7$, which is a contradiction."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Find the inverse of $\\begin{bmatrix} 5 & 0 \\\\ 0 & 1 \\end{bmatrix}$.",
