        "explanation": "$1 - 2(0.6)^2 = 1 - 0.72 = 0.28$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Evaluate $\\cos(15^\\circ)$ using $\\cos(30^\\circ/2)$.",
